column2: SELECT a.z, a.logMass, a.t_age_mean, a.metallicity_mean, a.dust1_mean, a.tau_mean, a.age_mean, a.ssfr_mean, d.w1flux, d.w1sigflux, d.w2flux, d.w2sigflux, d.w3flux, d.w3sigflux, d.w4flux, d.w4sigflux, p.psfFlux_u, p.psfFluxIvar_u, p.psfFlux_g, p.psfFluxIvar_g, p.psfFlux_r, p.psfFluxIvar_r, p.psfFlux_i, p.psfFluxIvar_i, p.psfFlux_z, p.psfFluxIvar_z into mydb.Train from stellarMassFSPSGranWideDust as a LEFT JOIN SpecPhotoAll as b on a.specObjID = b.specObjID LEFT JOIN WISE_xmatch as c on b.ObjID = c.sdss_objid LEFT JOIN WISE_allsky as d on c.wise_cntr = d.cntr LEFT JOIN PhotoObjAll as p on b.objID = p.objID ORDER BY b.objID ASC
